@@ set
    host            http://localhost:8000
    mobile_screen   540x960

Search component on local Firefox - small screen
    selenium firefox ${host}/dist/styleguide/3.search.html    ${mobile_screen}
        check test/visual/search.gspec --include "mobile,all" --exclude "toexclude,notfirefox"

Search component on local Chrome - small screen
    selenium chrome ${host}/dist/styleguide/3.search.html    ${mobile_screen}
        check test/visual/search.gspec --include "mobile,all" --exclude "toexclude,notchrome"
